tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE training_data (
    training_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    labeled_data_id INT,
    model_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (labeled_data_id) REFERENCES labeled_data(id),
    FOREIGN KEY (model_id) REFERENCES model(model_id)
);

CREATE TABLE labeled_training_data (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  data TEXT,
  label TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE training_data_labels (
  label_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  label_name TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE models (
  model_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  model_name TEXT,
  model_type TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE model_training_data (
  model_id INT,
  label_id INT,
  accuracy FLOAT,
  FOREIGN KEY (model_id) REFERENCES models(model_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (label_id) REFERENCES training_data_labels(label_id)
)

CREATE TABLE model_performance_metrics (
  model_id INT,
  precision FLOAT,
  recall FLOAT,
  f1_score FLOAT,
  FOREIGN KEY (model_id) REFERENCES models(model_id)
)
